 <text>
  <front>
   <head>SONG. Written in the Year 1733.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">THE heavy hours are almost past</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">That part my Love and me;</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">My longing eyes may hope at last,</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Their only wish to see.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">But how, my Delia, will you meet</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">The man you've lost so long?</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Will Love in all your pulses beat,</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">And tremble on your tongue?</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="3" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Will you in every look declare</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Your heart is still the same?</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And heal each idly anxious care</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Our fears in absence frame?</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="4" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="13" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Thus, Delia, thus I paint the scene,</l>
     <l n="14" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">When shortly we shall meet,</l>
     <l n="15" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And try what yet remains between</l>
     <l n="16" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Of loit'ring time to cheat.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="5" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="17" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">But if the dream that sooths my mind</l>
     <l n="18" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Shall false and groundless prove;</l>
     <l n="19" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">If I am doom'd at length to find</l>
     <l n="20" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">You have forgot to love;</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="6" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="21" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">All I of Venus ask, is this;</l>
     <l n="22" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">No more to let us join;</l>
     <l n="23" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">But grant me here the flatt'ring bliss,</l>
     <l n="24" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">To Die and Think you mine.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
  </body>
